org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.layout

Class TemporalIndexedLayout

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.layout.TemporalIndexedLayout
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphCollectionLayout<TemporalGraphHead,TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>, Layout<TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>, LogicalGraphLayout<TemporalGraphHead,TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>

    public class TemporalIndexedLayout
extends Object
implements LogicalGraphLayout<TemporalGraphHead,TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>, GraphCollectionLayout<TemporalGraphHead,TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>
    Represents a temporal graph or graph collection using one dataset per label and graph instance:
    1. a Map containing the graph label L as key and a graph head dataset G as value
    2. a Map containing the vertex label L as key and a vertex dataset V as value
    3. a Map containing the edge label L as key and a edge dataset E as value
